      <title>随着关键选举的临近，印度计划斥资 90 亿美元推动屋顶太阳能建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/india-plans-9-billion-rooftop-solar-push-as-key-elections-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度计划投资约 7500 亿卢比（90 亿美元），为 1000 万户家庭安装屋顶太阳能电池板，从而提振该国蓬勃发展的可再生能源产业中最薄弱的部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/india-plans-9-billion-rooftop-solar-push-as-key-elections-loom</guid>
